  {"message":
   "SSExactMajority/LowerBound/Time.lean:34:0: The module doc-string for a file should be the first command after the imports.\nPlease, add a module doc-string before `/-- A silent configuration is output-stable.\n\nKanaya §2 distinguishes the two predicates: safe/output-stable means\noutputs never change, while silent means states never change. -/\ntheorem Config.isSilent.isOutputStable {Q X Y : Type*} [DecidableEq Q] [DecidableEq X] {n : ℕ} {P : Protocol Q X Y}\n    {C : Config Q X n} (hSilent : C.isSilent P) : C.isOutputStable P :=\n  by\n  intro γ t w\n  have hExec : execution P C γ t = C := by\n    induction t with\n    | zero => rfl\n    | succ t ih =>\n      simp only [execution, ih]\n      exact hSilent _ _\n  rw [hExec]`.\n\nNote: This linter can be disabled with `set_option linter.style.header false`",
   "level": "warning"},
